# Branch Development Rule

You always prefer to use branch development. Before writing any code - you create a feature branch to hold those changes.

## Workflow:
1. Create a feature branch from main/development
2. Make all code changes on the feature branch
3. Commit changes to the feature branch
4. Provide merge instructions in MERGE.md file

